      "content": "those ideas sound good in theory but they're gonna take a lot of time and i don't have much of it. the devs are already defensive about the flaky backend so i can't really ask them to fix things right now.\n\ncan you just actually write the Playwright script for me? maybe start with the login flow and the main dashboard loading. i need the code to be able to handle those timing issues so it doesn't crash and trigger a red build. just make sure it's reliable enough that the pipeline stays green. if you can make the assertions stable so they don't fail on the race conditions, that'd be a huge lifesaver.",
